---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import DownloadButton from '../components/DownloadButton.astro';

const jsonLd = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@graph': [
    {
      '@type': 'SoftwareApplication',
      name: 'RTMify Trace',
      applicationCategory: 'BusinessApplication',
      operatingSystem: 'Windows, macOS, Linux',
      url: 'https://rtmify.io/trace',
      offers: [
        { '@type': 'Offer', name: 'Lab / Non-Commercial', price: '79', priceCurrency: 'USD', url: 'https://rtmify.io/pricing#trace' },
        { '@type': 'Offer', name: 'Individual', price: '99', priceCurrency: 'USD', url: 'https://rtmify.io/pricing#trace' },
        { '@type': 'Offer', name: 'Team / Commercial', price: '199', priceCurrency: 'USD', url: 'https://rtmify.io/pricing#trace' },
      ],
    },
    {
      '@type': 'SoftwareApplication',
      name: 'RTMify Live',
      applicationCategory: 'BusinessApplication',
      operatingSystem: 'Windows, macOS, Linux',
      url: 'https://rtmify.io/live',
      offers: [
        { '@type': 'Offer', name: 'Individual', price: '599', priceCurrency: 'USD', url: 'https://rtmify.io/pricing#live' },
        { '@type': 'Offer', name: 'Per Seat', price: '1499', priceCurrency: 'USD', url: 'https://rtmify.io/pricing#live' },
        { '@type': 'Offer', name: 'Site License', price: '4999', priceCurrency: 'USD', url: 'https://rtmify.io/pricing#live' },
      ],
    },
  ],
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="RTMify Pricing — Perpetual Licenses from $79, No Subscription"
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
  description="RTMify Template is free. RTMify Trace from $79. RTMify Live from $599. Perpetual licenses. No subscription required. Source code escrow."
>
  <Nav />

  <main class="flex-1">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="bg-[#1A1A2E] text-white py-16 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-family-display);">Pricing</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg">Perpetual licenses. No subscriptions. Run it locally.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Template -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#1A1A2E] rounded flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1A1A2E]">RTMify Template</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-[#DDDDDD] rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-6">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">Free</p>
            <p class="text-[#555555]">It is free forever. No account, no email, and no friction required. The four-tab .xlsx schema covers all six standards.</p>
          </div>
          <DownloadButton size="lg" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Trace -->
    <section id="trace" class="py-16 px-4 bg-[#F5F5F5] border-t border-[#DDDDDD]">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#1A1A2E] rounded flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1A1A2E]">RTMify Trace</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#555555] mb-8 ml-11">Trace generates a point-in-time RTM. Drop your spreadsheet and get a report. <a href="/trace" class="underline hover:text-[#1A1A2E]">Learn more →</a></p>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-5">

          <!-- Lab -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-[#DDDDDD] rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#555555] uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Lab / Non-Commercial</p>
            <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">$79</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#555555] mb-5">one-time &middot; +$10/yr maintenance</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[#555555] mb-8 flex-1">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Universities, research labs</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Personal non-commercial use</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> PDF, DOCX, Markdown output</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Industry profiles: generic, medical, aerospace, automotive</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Mac, Windows, Linux</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Perpetual license</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/4gMeVd88p7id7Id2zxe7m00" class="block text-center bg-[#1A1A2E] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg px-5 py-3 hover:bg-[#2A2A4E] transition-colors text-sm">Buy for $79</a>
          </div>

          <!-- Individual -->
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-[#1A1A2E] rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col relative">
            <span class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-[#1A1A2E] text-white text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Most popular</span>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#555555] uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Individual</p>
            <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">$99</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#555555] mb-5">one-time &middot; +$20/yr maintenance</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[#555555] mb-8 flex-1">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Commercial use, one person</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> PDF, DOCX, Markdown output</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Industry profiles: generic, medical, aerospace, automotive</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Mac, Windows, Linux</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> CI/CD <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded text-xs" style="font-family: var(--font-family-mono);">--strict</code> mode</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Perpetual license</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/cNiaEXewN4614w12zxe7m01" class="block text-center bg-[#1A1A2E] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg px-5 py-3 hover:bg-[#2A2A4E] transition-colors text-sm">Buy for $99</a>
          </div>

          <!-- Team -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-[#DDDDDD] rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#555555] uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Team / Commercial</p>
            <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">$199</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#555555] mb-5">one-time &middot; +$40/yr maintenance</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[#555555] mb-8 flex-1">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Unlimited seats, one org</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> PDF, DOCX, Markdown output</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Industry profiles: generic, medical, aerospace, automotive</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Mac, Windows, Linux</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> CI/CD <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded text-xs" style="font-family: var(--font-family-mono);">--strict</code> mode</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Perpetual license</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/bJe14n88p4610fLgqne7m02" class="block text-center bg-[#1A1A2E] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg px-5 py-3 hover:bg-[#2A2A4E] transition-colors text-sm">Buy for $199</a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Live -->
    <section id="live" class="py-16 px-4 bg-white border-t border-[#DDDDDD]">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#2A2A4E] rounded flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1A1A2E]">RTMify Live</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#555555] mb-8 ml-11">Live maintains a continuous product realization graph with sheet sync, source scanning, test ingestion, BOM and SBOM support, and a native MCP server. <a href="/live" class="underline hover:text-[#1A1A2E]">Learn more →</a></p>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-5">

          <!-- Individual -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-[#DDDDDD] rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#555555] uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Individual</p>
            <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">$599</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#555555] mb-5">one-time &middot; +$120/yr maintenance</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#555555] mb-5 leading-relaxed">Licensed for one quality engineer or lead engineer on one machine. The full graph runs on your laptop.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[#555555] mb-8 flex-1">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Google Sheets sync</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Git repo source scanning</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Test evidence ingestion (API + inbox)</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Hardware BOM + SBOM (CycloneDX, SPDX)</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Native MCP server</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Localhost dashboard</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Industry profiles</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Perpetual license</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/fZufZh4Wdbyt9Qlgqne7m03" class="block text-center bg-[#1A1A2E] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg px-5 py-3 hover:bg-[#2A2A4E] transition-colors text-sm">Buy for $599</a>
          </div>

          <!-- Per Seat -->
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-[#1A1A2E] rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col relative">
            <span class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-[#1A1A2E] text-white text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Most popular</span>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#555555] uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Per Seat</p>
            <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">$1,499<span class="text-lg font-normal text-[#555555]">/seat</span></p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#555555] mb-5">one-time &middot; +$500/yr per seat</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#555555] mb-5 leading-relaxed">Named engineers, any machine. The quality engineer configures the graph; each team member queries their own instance through MCP.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[#555555] mb-8 flex-1">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Everything in Individual</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Named user, any machine</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Team MCP access: engineers query the graph from their IDE</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Perpetual license</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/5kQ8wPcoF1XTaUp0rpe7m04" class="block text-center bg-[#1A1A2E] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg px-5 py-3 hover:bg-[#2A2A4E] transition-colors text-sm">Buy for $1,499 per seat</a>
          </div>

          <!-- Site -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-[#DDDDDD] rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#555555] uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Site License</p>
            <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">$4,999</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#555555] mb-5">one-time &middot; +$1,000/yr maintenance</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#555555] mb-5 leading-relaxed">Unlimited engineers, one org. Every team member runs Live. The product realization graph becomes shared infrastructure across your engineering organization.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[#555555] mb-8 flex-1">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Everything in Per Seat</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Unlimited users, one org</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Every engineer has MCP access to the graph</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Quality governs; the whole team queries</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#1A1A2E] font-bold shrink-0">✓</span> Perpetual license</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/28E5kDcoFdGBgeJca7e7m05" class="block text-center bg-[#1A1A2E] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg px-5 py-3 hover:bg-[#2A2A4E] transition-colors text-sm">Buy for $4,999</a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our commitments -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-[#F5F5F5] border-t border-[#DDDDDD]">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-8">Our commitments</h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

          <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#DDDDDD]">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-2">Perpetual license</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#555555]">You buy it once, you own it. The version you purchase works forever. Annual maintenance is optional. It covers updates and bug fixes.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#DDDDDD]">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-2">Source code escrow</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#555555]">This compliance tooling will never disappear out from under you.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#DDDDDD]">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-2">No subscription creep</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#555555]">We will never convert a perpetual license to a subscription, or raise maintenance prices on licenses already issued. The terms you buy under are the terms that apply.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-white border-t border-[#DDDDDD]">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-8">Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">

          <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#DDDDDD]">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">What does annual maintenance cover?</h3>
            <p class="text-[#555555]">New features, bug fixes, and compatibility updates for the year. If you skip a year, your license keeps working. You can renew at any time.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#DDDDDD]">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">What counts as "commercial use" for Trace?</h3>
            <p class="text-[#555555]">If you're using it at work (even at a non-profit) that's commercial. Lab/Non-Commercial is for students, academic researchers, and personal projects with no commercial application.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#DDDDDD]">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">Do all Live tiers get the same features?</h3>
            <p class="text-[#555555]">Yes. Sheet sync, git scanning, test ingestion, BOM/SBOM, MCP, dashboard, and industry profiles are all included in every tier on the same binary. The tiers control how many people in your organization can run it. Individual is one person on one machine. Per Seat is named engineers on any machine. Site License is your whole org.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#DDDDDD]">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">Why would I buy Site License instead of a few Per Seat licenses?</h3>
            <p class="text-[#555555]">At 4 seats, the Site License is cheaper. But the real reason is operational: with a Site License, every engineer can run Live and query the graph through MCP from their own IDE. The firmware engineer asks "what requirements does this file implement?" The test engineer asks "which test cases are suspect?" Nobody waits on the quality engineer to run a query for them. The quality engineer sets up the profile and schema. Everyone else talks to the graph directly.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#DDDDDD]">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">We need a purchase order or invoice. Can you do that?</h3>
            <p class="text-[#555555]">Yes. <a href="mailto:hello@rtmify.io" class="underline hover:text-[#1A1A2E]">Email us</a> with your org name and the license you need. We'll issue an invoice.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#DDDDDD]">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">Is there a trial?</h3>
            <p class="text-[#555555]">RTMify Trace allows one free successful run before a signed license is required. If you want to evaluate the schema first, the template is still the right starting point: it is free, and Trace reads that exact workbook format. RTMify Live does not have a free-run mode; it requires a license from the start, and purchases are covered by a 30-day money-back guarantee.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#DDDDDD]">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-1">What evidence types can Live ingest?</h3>
            <p class="text-[#555555]">Today: test execution results (JSON via API or file inbox), hardware BOMs (CSV), and software BOMs (CycloneDX JSON, SPDX JSON). The inbox accepts all types in a single directory: drop a file and Live detects the type and routes it. We're adding more evidence types on a continuous basis.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
